experience.description:
Tasks performed:
1. Search and selection of IT specialists using Internet resources and professional communities;
2. Labor market analysis, building partnerships with business customers;
3. Maintaining internal reporting. A full cycle of recruitment for open vacancies. Personnel evaluation, conducting interviews with candidates using various methods. Coordination of interviews, collection of recommendations. Creating the company's image in the Internet space.
4. Search and selection of IT specialists of all levels (business analyst, 1C developer, QA Lead, Product Owner, java developer, frontend developer, head of business analysis, Data Scientist from 0 to PRO);
5. Publication of vacancies on search resources and direct search of profiles in open sources/ social networks /professional communities

They performed the role of a recruitment agency, carried out the selection of IT specialists in various organizations, such as VTB Bank, Alfa-bank, and so on. Search for candidates from various countries (Russia, Ukraine, Belarus, Kazakhstan, Armenia, America, Europe, India, China etc.)
